{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/BOJ/2512/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Seize the day","author":"이규빈","siteUrl":"https://gatsby-starter-bee.netlify.com","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"JaeYeopHan/gatsby-starter-bee"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"jbee"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b16ab27e-37d4-5158-be53-3f325b9a653b","excerpt":"문제 설명 예를 들어, 전체 국가예산이 485이고 4개 지방의 예산요청이 각각 120, 110, 140, 150이라고 하자. 이 경우, 상한액을 127로 잡으면, 위의 요청들에 대해서 각각 120, 110, 127, 127을 배정하고 그 합이 484로 가능한 최대가 된다.  입력 출력 즉 , 120 은 127 보다 작음으로 유지 110 은 127 보다 작으니까 유지 140 은 127 보다 크니까 127로 계산 150 은 127 보다 크니까 12…","html":"<h1 id=\"문제-설명\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85\" aria-label=\"문제 설명 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 설명</h1>\n<p>예를 들어, 전체 국가예산이 485이고 4개 지방의 예산요청이 각각 120, 110, 140, 150이라고 하자. 이 경우, 상한액을 127로 잡으면, 위의 요청들에 대해서 각각 120, 110, 127, 127을 배정하고 그 합이 484로 가능한 최대가 된다. </p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>입력</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">4\n120 110 140 150\n485</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>출력</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">127</code></pre></div>\n<p>즉 ,<br>\n120 은 127 보다 작음으로 유지<br>\n110 은 127 보다 작으니까 유지<br>\n140 은 127 보다 크니까 127로 계산<br>\n150 은 127 보다 크니까 127로 계산  </p>\n<h1 id=\"나의-문제풀이\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98-%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C%ED%92%80%EC%9D%B4\" aria-label=\"나의 문제풀이 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>나의 문제풀이</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>보자마자 이분탐색이 생각났다.</li>\n<li>기준을 <strong>합</strong> 으로 생각했다. 유사한 문제로는 <a href=\"https://www.acmicpc.net/problem/2805\">나무자르기문제</a></li>\n<li>answer가 커질수록, 전체 값도 커진다.</li>\n<li>이를 기준으로 tmp<em>total</em>monny를 선언하여 원래의 money_total=485 와 비교하며 start 와  end 를 점차 좁혀나간다</li>\n<li>이후 start가 end 보다 커지는 순간이 답이다! </li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> sys\nn <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token builtin\">input</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nk <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">list</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token builtin\">map</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token builtin\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>sys<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>stdin<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>readline<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>split<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\ntotal_money <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token builtin\">input</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nstart <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\nend <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">max</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>k<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\ntmp_total_money<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">while</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>start<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span>end<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    \n    tmp_total_money<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n    mid <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>start<span class=\"token operator\">+</span>end<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">//</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span> \n    \n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> k<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i<span class=\"token operator\">>=</span>mid<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n            tmp_total_money<span class=\"token operator\">+=</span>mid\n            \n        <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n            tmp_total_money<span class=\"token operator\">+=</span>i\n             \n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> tmp_total_money<span class=\"token operator\">></span>total_money<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token comment\">#예상값이 더 큰 경우</span>\n        end <span class=\"token operator\">=</span>mid<span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> \n        start<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>mid<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>start<span class=\"token operator\">></span>end<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>end<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    \n    </code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"백준 2512번 파이썬","date":"September 12, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/BOJ/2512/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/BOJ/1654/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"백준 1654번 파이썬"}},"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["2486386679","3128451518"]}